  "text": "The aim of this study was to generate a rat model of preeclampsia by an administration of ultra-low-dose LPS around early placentation, and to assess the contribution of TLR4 signaling to the development of preeclampsia. Concerning that placentation in the rat starts immediately after implantation between GDs 4 and 5 [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , pregnant rats were administrated with LPS on GD 5.",
